149
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,960
Those clients you worked on these days

150
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,320
have all entered the approval process as well.

151
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,639
Your performance for this month is secured.

152
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:34,559
You can rest assured and take an annual leave.

153
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:37,960
Go have fun with your newlywed husband.

154
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:40,000
Sorry, Ji.

155
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,016
Compared to my best friend,

156
00:10:42,016 --> 00:10:44,559
you have to step aside for now.

157
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,832
Lean on me.

158
00:10:50,752 --> 00:10:53,360
Where do you want to go for fun?
I have a holiday now.

159
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,720
We'll go wherever you want to go.

160
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,120
I want to go alone.

161
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:02,440
No. I'll be worried.

162
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:07,639
I've been with Qi Yu for so many years.

163
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:10,159
We've been through so much together.

164
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:15,639
It's also time for me to sort things out alone.

165
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:22,279
Don't worry. I won't stay single forever,

166
00:11:22,279 --> 00:11:24,279
or get discouraged.

167
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:28,159
I'll be back myself when I'm better.

168
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:30,472
Just like last time.

169
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:38,919
Someone said,

170
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:41,159
as long as there's a holiday,

171
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:44,720
she would go on vacation with Ji.

172
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:49,679
Alright, don't worry about me.

173
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:52,559
I just want to be alone for a while.

174
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:56,360
How can I not worry?

175
00:12:02,039 --> 00:12:03,559
I've been waiting for you.

176
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:04,879
Good news.

177
00:12:04,879 --> 00:12:06,679
The new energy company
you personally negotiated with

178
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:08,759
is going through
the financing approval process.

179
00:12:08,759 --> 00:12:11,200
As long as we secure this top-notch big client,

180
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:14,240
it also lays a foundation
for the future development

181
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,639
of Ji'an branch.

182
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:17,440
When the comprehensive cooperation starts,

183
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:21,120
we won't have to worry about our performance
for quite a while in the future.

184
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:23,080
Sounds like good news.

185
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,840
However, you have to keep a closer eye on it.

186
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:25,840
Rest assured.

187
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:28,080
By the way, I've taken an annual leave.

188
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:30,200
Together with the Mid-Autumn Festival holiday.

189
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:34,960
Mr. Zhao, please be more attentive
in the upcoming period.

190
00:12:37,376 --> 00:12:41,608
Mr. Zhao? You just said Mr. Zhao?

191
00:12:41,888 --> 00:12:43,976
What does that mean?

192
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,840
Honey, let me tie the apron on you,

193
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,279
so you won't get your white shirt dirty.

194
00:12:49,279 --> 00:12:51,399
It's so delicious.

195
00:12:52,288 --> 00:12:53,320
I've looked up the information.

196
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,279
Having hot pot once in a while is okay.

197
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:56,840
I've already told you so.

198
00:12:56,840 --> 00:13:00,279
And having one or two cups of milk tea
occasionally is okay.

199
00:13:00,279 --> 00:13:02,279
I've already told you so.

200
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:04,960
This milk tea is almost finished.
I'll order you another one.

201
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,200
Get me a cold one.

202
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,232
No way.

203
00:13:07,232 --> 00:13:09,240
Alright then. Get me a warm one.

204
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:13,919
Both eating hot pot and drinking milk tea
are okay for me.

205
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:16,279
But there's something wrong with you.

206
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:18,480
What's wrong with me?

207
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:21,879
Is getting promoted
to a department manager that happy?

208
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:24,720
Setting up such a big table just for me?

209
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:26,728
Well, what else?

210
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:29,919
To put it big,

211
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:32,600
my career has achieved a milestone success.

212
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,200
To put it small, from now on,

213
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:36,608
I'm finally on an equal footing with you.

214
00:13:36,608 --> 00:13:37,679
Congratulations.

215
00:13:37,679 --> 00:13:39,039
Such a great joy.

216
00:13:39,039 --> 00:13:41,000
Let alone having a hot pot
or a cup of milk tea,

217
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:43,720
even if you want to go to the club
tonight and see the blond guy,

218
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:46,080
- I'll keep you company.
- I didn't see him last time.

219
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,759
That's more like it.

220
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:50,080
Besides, that blonde guy
is not as handsome as your husband.

221
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,168
Exactly.

222
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:58,240
Come on, have a piece of meat.

223
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,240
I'm much better now. You'd eat.

224
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:04,000
I knew it. Ji always keeps his word.

225
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,639
He doesn't make empty promises.

226
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:09,080
Don't compliment Ji here to me.

227
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:12,200
You're the only one who doesn't know
that Ji made you the department manager

228
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:15,080
just so he could put all the work onto you,

229
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:17,159
and then he can go on annual leave,

230
00:14:17,159 --> 00:14:20,039
taking his wife to go have fun.

231
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:32,600
Where's my milk tea? Did you order it?

232
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:35,639
I'm not ordering anymore.
Too much milk tea is bad for your health.

233
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:39,159
Believe it or not,
I will pour this hot pot on your face.

234
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,792
It's already on the way.

235
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:46,952
Keep eating.

236
00:14:48,692 --> 00:14:50,760
[Be happy]

237
00:15:05,587 --> 00:15:09,152
♫ I can always see the faint glimmer of light ♫

238
00:15:09,152 --> 00:15:12,712
♫ Flowing through the gaps between my fingers ♫

239
00:15:13,504 --> 00:15:15,424
♫ As the wind along the way ♫

240
00:15:15,424 --> 00:15:18,400
♫ Accompanying me through yesterday ♫

241
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:22,920
♫ Rushing towards
all the destinations of the future ♫

242
00:15:23,264 --> 00:15:26,280
♫ Sweat poured down every step ♫

243
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:30,568
♫ Chasing happiness with all my heart ♫

244
00:15:31,584 --> 00:15:34,504
♫ Every scene passed by ♫

245
00:15:35,412 --> 00:15:38,504
♫ We know there's a new beginning in life ♫

246
00:15:38,963 --> 00:15:42,408
♫ Refreshing all the unknowns ♫

247
00:15:44,799 --> 00:15:47,519
Hello, can you take a picture
of me and my wife?

248
00:15:47,519 --> 00:15:49,279
- Thank you.
- Sure.

249
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:51,336
Let's take a picture together.

250
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:54,399
Get closer and smile.

251
00:15:54,399 --> 00:15:56,552
Go check it.

252
00:16:00,879 --> 00:16:03,480
It's nice, thank you.

253
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:05,672
How do you think?

254
00:16:09,152 --> 00:16:10,159
Thank you.

255
00:16:10,159 --> 00:16:12,168
No problem.

256
00:16:18,399 --> 00:16:20,919
Ji said you could find him by this cat.

257
00:16:20,919 --> 00:16:22,984
Go for it.

258
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:28,360
I'll hold this for you for now.

259
00:16:42,759 --> 00:16:46,440
The story begins with that cat.

260
00:17:04,628 --> 00:17:08,296
[You complete me.]

261
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:12,192
Shall we go back and look for it?

262
00:17:12,192 --> 00:17:13,856
